videos.description: LeBron James gets things started early as he pulls up for a long, step-back jumper over Bam Adebayo.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (LeBron drains deep jumpshot over Bam) 2020/9/30 ESHEET

videos.headline: LeBron drains deep jumpshot over Bam

videos.description: Jimmy Butler sends a smooth pass to Jae Crowder who pulls up for a 3-pointer to give the Heat a 13-point lead early.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Butler slings a nice pass to Crowder for 3) 2020/9/30 ESHEET

videos.headline: Butler slings a nice pass to Crowder for 3

videos.description: President Barack Obama, Shaquille O'Neal, Robin Roberts, Kareem Abdul-Jabbar and several others were in remote attendance for Game 1 of Lakers vs. Heat.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Obama, Shaq, Kareem highlight star-studded virtual crowd) 2020/9/30 ESHEET

videos.headline: Obama, Shaq, Kareem highlight star-studded virtual crowd

videos.description: Tyler Herro and Jimmy Butler connect on two consecutive possessions for a pair of slick baskets.
videos.headline: Herro drains back-to-back buckets

videos.description: Alex Caruso takes the pass from LeBron James and then drives to the hoop showing off a nice fake.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Caruso fakes, switches hands for two) 2020/9/30 ESHEET

videos.headline: Caruso fakes, switches hands for two

videos.description: Jimmy Butler appears to roll his ankle late in the first half, dropping to the hardwood in pain and shortly after limps off the court to the locker room.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Butler appears to hurt ankle, heads to locker room) 2020/9/30 ESHEET

videos.headline: Butler appears to hurt ankle, heads to locker room

videos.description: Kyle Kuzma fights his way through traffic and quickly passes the ball off to Anthony Davis who rushes in from the corner for a slam dunk.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Kuzma hands it off to AD for the slam) 2020/9/30 ESHEET

videos.headline: Kuzma hands it off to AD for the slam

videos.description: Kyle Kuzma puts up the oop and LeBron James flies in from the other end of the court to throw down a beautiful reverse slam, but it doesn't count.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (LeBron throws down filthy reverse after halftime buzzer) 2020/9/30 ESHEET

videos.headline: LeBron throws down filthy reverse after halftime buzzer

videos.description: Anthony Davis doesn't quit as he battles through the Heat's defense for third-quarter basket.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (AD outworks Miami's D for big bucket) 2020/9/30 ESHEET

videos.headline: AD outworks Miami's D for big bucket

videos.description: Dwight Howard slings a pass to Anthony Davis under the hoop and AD rises up for a two-handed hammer.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (AD piles on with baseline slam) 2020/9/30 ESHEET

videos.headline: AD piles on with baseline slam

videos.description: Anthony Davis reflects on the Lakers' Game 1 win over the Heat and talks about his personal feat of 34 points in his first career NBA Finals game.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NBA Interview (AD: 'This is the moment I've waited for my entire career') 2020/9/30 ESHEET

videos.headline: AD: 'This is the moment I've waited for my entire career'

videos.description: Kentavious Caldwell-Pope comes from behind to block Tyler Herro at the rim with under five minutes remaining in Game 1.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (KCP rejects Herro at the rim late in the 4th) 2020/9/30 ESHEET

videos.headline: KCP rejects Herro at the rim late in the 4th

videos.description: Jimmy Butler reaffirms that the Heat will be ready for battle with the Lakers with or without Goran Dragic, but also explains there are a number of aspects the Heat must improve upon before Game 2.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NBA Presser (Butler reacts to reports of Dragic's injury) 2020/09/30

videos.headline: Butler reacts to reports of Dragic's injury

videos.description: Tim Legler says Game 1 was a battle of a "heavyweight vs. a lightweight" but still believes Miami has a chance to win the title if they put their eye on the prize.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NBA Analysis (Legler saw the Heat lose 'spirit’ in Game 1) 2020/9/30 ESHEET

videos.headline: Legler saw the Heat lose 'spirit' in Game 1

videos.description: LeBron James takes the pass from Rajon Rondo while driving to the rim and throws down a perfect double-clutch dunk in the fourth quarter of Game 1.
videos.headline: LeBron's smooth, double-clutch jam
